This archive contains new 1999 season far more detailed cars, the up-to-date Teams and Drivers files
(though, because VGP doesn't simulate drivers' injuries, the 1999 season cannot be properly
reproduced) and some car setups of mine so that people can understand how to do them.
The files must replace the corresponding ones in the corresponding drawers.

